        <h1>Miami Marketing Agency Pricing 2026: The Honest Breakdown</h1>
        <p class="lead">Most Miami marketing agencies refuse to publish what they charge. We audited five of them, and built this guide so any small operator can compare apples to apples before booking a sales call.</p>
